1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:08,000
Scratch Wallet is a risk-capped autonomous DeFi micro-wallet by Mathieu D. WEILL.

2
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:18,000
Users fund a tiny isolated wallet instead of connecting their main wallet.

3
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:32,000
The agent scans opportunities, simulates execution costs, blocks unsafe approvals, and rejects most candidates.

4
00:00:32,000 --> 00:00:48,000
The core product metaphor: a lottery ticket that knows when not to play.

5
00:00:48,000 --> 00:01:05,000
Every played opportunity, skipped opportunity, blocked rug, and stop event can be anchored on HashKey Chain.

6
00:01:05,000 --> 00:01:25,000
Autonomous finance should start with bounded downside.
